div.div: Created new branch refactor in shinyPy/porto-company

Refactor metadata management for app routes
Centralizes metadata and viewport configuration in a new metadata.ts file and replaces per-page metadata exports with generateMetadata factories for static routes. This improves maintainability and reduces duplication across layout and page components.
